{"tid":1101710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美商務部列37中国機構危險名單    7港企上榜","createTime":"2019-04-11T08:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T14:35:20.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c8e9a69da2f6694b16c1e5a25f3e2b9c543da935","tid":1101710,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T08:22:51.000Z","msg":"美國商務部將37間中國企業和學術機構，列入美國企業應謹慎對待的「未經核實」實體的危險名單。 當中包括本港的7間公司，並於周四生效。<br />\n<br />\n本港方面有7間公司列入名單， 包括優聯國際供應鏈、 韜博盛科技、香港恒宇倉儲物流、遠航科技香港、以及陞運物流、Swelatel Technology Limited、Universe Market Limited、<br />\n<br />\n內地名單上其中一家公司是愛信（南通）汽車技術中心有限公司，是一家日本汽車零部件製造商的中國子公司。另一家是北京八億時空液晶材料科技有限公司，該公司已經獲得了高端屏幕技術的專利。<br />\n<br />\n學校方面，上榜的包括長春應用化學研究所，該研究所專門從事物理和化學研究。而廣東工業大學、中國人民大學、上海同濟大學及位於西安的兩間學校亦列入名單。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述美國商務部負責出口管理的前助理部長沃爾夫表示，清單意味美國公司將謹慎對待這些機構，「儘管這不是禁運，但因為麻煩，有時供應商會把它當作禁運。它的實際效果大於法律效果」。<br />\n<br />\n列入上述名單的還包括阿聯酋的4間、馬來西亞2間和印尼1間機構。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/977500-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%BE%8E%E5%95%86%E5%8B%99%E9%83%A8%E5%88%9737%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE+7%E6%B8%AF%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%8A%E6%A6%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F977500-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%258B%2599%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%259737%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A7%258B%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%259A%25AA%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%2B7%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BC%2581%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25A6%259C&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=16adb370\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F977500-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%258B%2599%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%259737%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A7%258B%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%259A%25AA%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%2B7%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BC%2581%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25A6%259C&h=d183a18c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/977500-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E7%BE%8E%E5%95%86%E5%8B%99%E9%83%A8%E5%88%9737%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE+7%E6%B8%AF%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%8A%E6%A6%9C</a>"},{"pid":"9a8c46434c6f4f31545999f028d90dc3706bb33c","tid":1101710,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:10:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d04bc5cff72e0a6a0fb0880034e20e6760f4bc2","tid":1101710,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:36:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本港方面有7間公司列入名單， 包括優聯國際供應鏈、 韜博盛科技、香港恒宇倉儲物流、遠航科技香港、以及陞運物流、Swelatel Technology Limited、Universe Market Limited</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCIA <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849c0d49ed3bf768fc9efb3081b12369c6b1ad5f","tid":1101710,"uid":36134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:40:53.000Z","msg":"埋大都應該上榜啦<br />\n成間紅校黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c4ee3ce3da0b297fd6e3c0339b96d2c5291564","tid":1101710,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"849c0d49ed3bf768fc9efb3081b12369c6b1ad5f","tid":1101710,"uid":36134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:40:53.000Z","msg":"埋大都應該上榜啦<br />\n成間紅校黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:41:36.000Z","msg":"理大, 浸大, 港大, 中大都應該上"},{"pid":"570a341a5fa79cf004c030dd672925588588a73c","tid":1101710,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:45:02.000Z","msg":"共享支那人榮耀時刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44c20bcd40a16efb7a8f9644617aac18cf9bd90",